# PORTFOLIO-REQ-03A — Development Maturity Baseline Report

Status: DEVELOPMENT_BASELINE_ESTABLISHED

Root versioning state: `/opt/Axodus` is not a Git repository. Global portfolio files are local/unversioned.

## Methodology

This report introduces D-level development maturity as a second axis beside L-level organizational maturity.

Evidence reviewed:

- root portfolio status, roadmap, maturity register and blocker register;
- portfolio normalization, validation refresh and gated advancement reports;
- cross-nucleus opportunity, dependency, ownership and boundary reports;
- local `.instructions` status, validation, handoff, blocker and maturity assessment files;
- repository structure, source footprint, tests, docs, package scripts and implemented product surfaces.

The assessment is conservative. A D-level measures implementation depth, not production readiness. D3 does not authorize trading, DEX execution, wallet signing, treasury movement, settlement, payout, governance execution or production operation.

## Nuclei Reviewed

Core, Governance, Documentation, Dex, Defi, AxodusAPP, Business, Marketplace, Academy, Mining, ACS, Trading, BBA-Agency, Lottery.

