- Business: L4 Consolidated / D2.
- Defi: L4 Readiness / D2.
- Documentation: L4 Readiness / D2.

Low L / higher D:

- Trading: L4 Candidate / D3.

Balanced:

- Core, Governance, Dex, AxodusAPP, Marketplace, Academy, Mining, ACS, BBA-Agency, Lottery.

